# Build context hygiene — backend/Dockerfile uses the repo ROOT as context
# (it builds the frontend and embeds it). Keep node_modules, VCS, and local
# artifacts out so builds stay fast on Render and locally.
**/node_modules
frontend/dist
backend/bin
.git
.claude
docs
tests
*.log
# never ship local secrets into a build context
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
